Title: Unearthed Troublemakers
Description:
The earth elementals are not just trying to repel us, they're destroying artifacts and equipment, too! It's as though they've been programmed to destroy anything titan...

We're holding them off, but we can't continue to study this site while they're here. Please help us push them back so we can have some exploring room!
ObjectivesText: Kill 12 Earth Elementals in the Life Vault Ruins.
